### 🔍 Image Breakdown (for your HTML/CSS/JS build)

Here's how you can **structure your frontend** using this image:

#### 1. `TopBar`

```html
<div class="top-bar">
  <h1>My Smart Farm 🌾</h1>
  <div class="weather">☀️ 32°C, Sunny</div>
</div>
```

#### 2. `Stats Cards`

```html
<div class="stats">
  <div class="card moisture">Soil Moisture: 68%</div>
  <div class="card ph">pH Level: 6.4</div>
  <div class="card crop-health">🟢🟡🔴 Crop Health</div>
</div>
```

#### 3. `AI Suggestion Box`

```html
<div class="ai-box">
  🤖 Recommended Crop: Maize <br>
  Ideal Conditions: Moderate Water, pH 6–7
</div>
```

#### 4. `Farm Map`

```html
<div class="map-section">
  <img src="farm-map.png" alt="Farm Sensor Map">
</div>
```

#### 5. `Analytics Charts`

```html
<div class="charts">
  <canvas id="yieldChart"></canvas>
  <canvas id="waterUsageChart"></canvas>
</div>
```

